<normalizedToken id="BFC2FD2ECF66AAE5EC0769C9647784A1" originalValue="Gärten" pageId="null" pageNumber="386">Gaerten</normalizedToken>
(Smith 1951, Morrison 1959).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="6E34E870C3F7E7EA7EC68944158A651A" pageId="null" pageNumber="386">
<emphasis id="428ABE70D20A50F96DF2E1F882B160C8" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="386">Standort.</emphasis>
